  <refnamediv>
    <refname>channel_capacity</refname>
    <refpurpose>Channel capacity</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>


<refsynopsisdiv>
   <title>Calling Sequence</title>
   <synopsis>
   c = channel_capacity(snr,B)
   
   </synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsection>
   <title>Parameters</title>
   <variablelist>
   <varlistentry><term>snr:</term>
      <listitem><para> Signal to noise power ratio (linear scale)</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   <varlistentry><term>B:</term>
      <listitem><para> Channel bandwidth, in Hz (default is 1 Hz)</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   <varlistentry><term>c:</term>
      <listitem><para> Channel capacity, in bits/s</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
</refsection>

<refsection>
   <title>Description</title>
   <para>
Computes the ideal AWGN channel capacity, in bits:
<latex>$$c = B\log_2(1+\textrm{SNR})$$</latex>
   </para>
   <para>
</para>
</refsection>

